resources.string: Are you sure want to submit the exam. Please make sure after clicking Finish button, you cannot make any changes. Please click on Confirm for exam submission.

2.You can flag any of the question you want.
3. you can clear answers if you do not wish to submit any of the responses provided.
4. If you drop this exam,it will not be submitted, and result will not br generated.
5.you can finish this exam even if any questions are un-attempted.
6.Once the exam is finished,it cannot be resumed.
